Package: freestatemoney
Type: Package
Title: Load and Parse Maryland Campaign Finance Data
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("NewsAppsUMD", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dpwillis@umd.edu")
    )
Description: Provides functions to download, parse, and analyze campaign
    finance data from the Maryland State Board of Elections. Downloads bulk
    data directly from the Campaign Reporting Information System (CRIS) API
    and returns tidy data frames for committees, contributions/loans, and
    expenditures.
